  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/wearables/\" rel=\"tag\">佩戴产品</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/26/google-now-inviting-developers-to-buy-glass/\"><img alt=\"Google Glass invitation for developers\" src=\"http://hss-prod.hss.aol.com/hss/storage/adam/669078482bc5470b2defb616c2927b10/google-glass-developer-invitation.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n在发布了 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/googleglass\">Google Glass</a> SDK 预览、向所有开发者开放 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/24/google-opens-mirror-api-to-all/\">Mirror API</a> 之后，自然而然地，接下来就是把 Google Glass 送到更多的应用开发者手中了。而 Google 也正是这么打算的，他们已于今日向开发者送出了购买 Google Glass Explorer Edition 的邀请（见上图），希望后者能与其一道迈出「发展 Glass 的下一步」。目前我们还不清楚此次 Explorer 的项目范围究竟扩大了多少，主站编辑已经联系了 Google，有回应后我们再告知各位。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/11/25/google-now-inviting-developers-to-buy-glass/\">Engadget</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/26/google-now-inviting-developers-to-buy-glass/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20776280/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/26/google-now-inviting-developers-to-buy-glass/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
